                    <h3>IoT & Smart Systems

                    </h3>
                    <p>Developing intelligent, interconnected devices for smart cities, healthcare, and automation.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="research_item" style="--bg-color:#002147;">
                <div class="image_wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/d.jpg" alt="Research 4">
                </div>
                <div class="text_content">
                    <h3>Human-Computer Interaction (HCI)

                    </h3>
                    <p>Enhancing user experience with intuitive interfaces, AR/VR, and assistive technologies.

                    </p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="research_item" style="--bg-color:#002147;">
                <div class="image_wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/e.jpg" alt="Research 5">
                </div>
                <div class="text_content">
                    <h3>Autonomous Systems & Robotics

                    </h3>
                    <p>Designing AI-powered robots for automation, navigation, and real-world problem-solving.

                    </p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="research_item" style="--bg-color:#004C99;">
                <div class="image_wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/f.jpg" alt="Research 6">
                </div>
                <div class="text_content">
                    <h3>Cybersecurity & Ethical Hacking

                    </h3>
                    <p>Strengthening digital security through penetration testing, threat analysis, and cryptography.
                    </p>
